ygData.messageBody:
Jiya,
I have noticed a lot of people on Fennin Ro, and Solusek Ro (sp)....but
am I the only one on this list that is on Cazic? Well...if anyone wants to
hunt I am 8th level and, unfortunately for my lack of xps, hunt in the
Karanas. I am gonna do the old fashioned thing and save all my pennies for a
tommy. I'll prolly be about 13th level before I can get one but hey, that's
the point. ;-}~

Tyveris,
Aspiring Samurai (in training)
